  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2fe0abe2bc63b4548846bb100704dbfe, type: 3}
  m_Name: ManagerOptionA
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
  - Now here comes the scary news.
  - Recently, there have been reports of evil Dream Worms disguising themselves as
    customers.
  - They will look similar to the real thing, so use the tools on the right to help
    you verify their integrity!
  - From the top, the first icon will allow you to pull up the customer's ID card.
    Make sure they look EXACTLY like the picture.
  - The second icon will let you flip the light switch. Some Dream Worms will look
    different in the dark.
  - 'The third icon is my secret weapon: the Diabolo''s Wiener Donut!'
  - It is super spicy, but some Dream Worms can't feel spice at all.
  - The fourth icon is the most dangerous. It is a gun! If you suspect that a customer
    is an imposter, shoot them!
  - Of course, please don't shoot the real customers.
  - Oh, and one more thing.
  - Everytime you get an order wrong, shoot a real customer, or accidentally serve
    a Dream Worm, your sanity will deteriorate.
  - If your sanity hits zero, you will die.
  - But I'm sure you are smart enough to handle this. Good luck!
  responses: []
